The paper discusses the use of artificial neural networks and spiking neural networks for efficient computation, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the use of adaptive spiking neurons, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper presents results on benchmarks, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper discusses the use of spiking neurons for asynchronous communication, which is a topic in control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of spiking neurons for image recognition, which is a topic in computer vision (cs.CV).
